'''Reenogga Personal Services, Cubed''', also called '''Reenogga Personal Services³''', '''RPS Cubed''', or just '''RPS''', was a firm of "equalizers" owned and operated by the [[Reenogga Sisters]], former members of the [[Skine Bounty Hunter College]]. Their offices were located in the ''[[Death Mark]]'' aboard the [[Zirtran's Anchor/Legends|''Zirtran's Anchor'']] [[Space station/Legends|space station]].<ref name="ZA">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

RPS offered their protection, for a fee, to clients against virtually any threat from illegal bounty hunting to assassination. RPS maintained a number of transport ships and [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] for off-station duties. They would often help [[Quink]], a friend of one of the sisters, to get his cousin [[Padda]] out of trouble.<ref name="ZA" />

